cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.GT, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new approach for playing Go using a deep alternative neural network and long-term evaluation. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Game Theory (cs.GT), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
